                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9538" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0318</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">930 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“晨”向未来，笃志前行——晨鸣纸业的ESG探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Morning” to the Future, Forward with Commitment - Chenming Paper&#39;s ESG Exploration Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱强，许琦，田敏霞，陈姝屹，乔玉洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东晨鸣纸业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">晨鸣纸业；ESG体系；探索历程；ESG议题</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chenming Paper; ESG system; Journey of discovery; ESG issues</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2004年联合国全球契约计划首次提出ESG概念，该概念是衡量企业环境、社会、治理绩效的企业评价标准。2012年香港联合交易所发布的《ESG报告指引》鼓励了我国上市公司发布ESG报告。近年来，随着“社会责任”、“双碳环保”等话题热度飙升，资本市场对ESG理念的关注度越来越高，实施ESG战略已成为企业可持续发展的必选题。本案例以山东晨鸣纸业集团股份有限公司（以下简称“晨鸣纸业”）为研究对象，描绘了晨鸣纸业以ESG理念为核心，探索出一条具有公司特色的ESG实践道路。本案例通过描述晨鸣纸业实施ESG战略的动因、过程及成果，旨在帮助学生了解ESG的内涵、实施动因及具体措施，加深学生对利益相关者理论、可持续发展等理论的认识，启发学生思考实施ESG战略的必要性与现实意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2004, the United Nations Global Compact Program first proposed the concept of ESG, which is a corporate evaluation standard for measuring the environmental, social and governance performance of enterprises, and in 2012, the Hong Kong Stock Exchange issued the “Guidelines on ESG Reporting” to encourage listed companies in China to publish ESG reports. In recent years, with the soaring popularity of topics such as “social responsibility” and “dual-carbon environmental protection”, the capital market has been paying more and more attention to ESG concepts, and the implementation of ESG strategies has become a must for the sustainable development of enterprises. This case takes Shandong Chenming Paper Group Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as “Chenming Paper”) as the object of study, and depicts Chenming Paper&#39;s exploration of a company-specific ESG practice path with ESG concepts as the core. By describing the motivation, process and results of Chenming Paper&#39;s ESG strategy, the case aims to help students understand the connotation, motivation and specific measures of ESG, deepen students&#39; understanding of stakeholder theory, sustainable development and other theories, and inspire students to think about the necessity and significance of the implementation of ESG strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者理论；可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-04</td>
                            </tr>
